thread.title: BRIEF-Winsan Shanghai Medical Science and Technology to acquire more 14 pct stake in health industry firm

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Winsan Shanghai Medical Science and Technology to acquire more 14 pct stake in health industry firm

organizations.name: winsan shanghai medical science and technology co ltd

text:
Feb 5(Reuters) - Winsan Shanghai Medical Science and Technology Co Ltd
* Says it plans to acquire more 14 percent stake in Anhui-based health industry firm (target firm), at the price of 9.6 million yuan
* Says it will hold 84 percent stake in target firm, up from 70 percent
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/C3r4F8
